      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA'S HASTY (3) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at Q Parklands over 520m behind Beautiful Child (30.24) in a Grade 5. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Has ability and looks hard to stop. ROCKABYE BABY (7) was well in the market last time but only managed fourth (30.67), beaten 13 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Cannot be left out. TWO FACED GWEN (5) box seated before sticking on well to finish 2.5 lengths away in third (20.15) at this track in a P5 over 366m. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in two starts. Will give a great sight again. HOT PINK DOUBLE (1) can improve on an unplaced run here last time out.",
